  "title": "⭐️ Event Sales Team",
  "description": "<p><em><strong>Want a job that’s social, energetic, and not stuck behind a desk?</strong></em></p><p><br /><br />If you enjoy meeting new people, working in exciting environments, and being part of a fun, driven team — this could be for you!</p><p><br />We’re growing our Event Sales Team and looking for fresh grads, students, and career switchers to join us at roadshows, pop-up events, and exhibitions across Singapore. You’ll represent brands, work with a supportive crew, and pick up real-life skills you can actually use.</p><p><br /></p><p>✨ <em>No experience? No problem. Full training provided.</em></p><p><br /><br /></p><p><u>What You’ll Be Doing</u></p><p>• Chat with customers and create great first impressions</p><p>• Introduce products and services that you are representing</p><p>• Work with teammates in fast-paced, live event settings</p><p>• Join team outings, bonding sessions, and workshops</p><p>• Learn leadership and team skills as you grow</p><p><br /><br /></p><p><u>Why You’ll Like This Role</u></p><p>• No boring desk job — every day is different</p><p>• Fun, friendly team with hands-on guidance</p><p>• Build confidence, communication, and sales skills</p><p>• Clear growth path (we promote from within)</p><p>• Local & overseas travel opportunities for top performers ✈️</p><p><br /></p><p><br /><u>Growth Path</u></p><p>Junior role (sales & mareting) → Team Lead → Project Manager</p><p><strong>We value attitude, effort, and growth mindset over experience.</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><u>Who We’re Looking For</u><br /><br />• <strong>Enjoys talking to people</strong></p><p><strong>• Open-minded, positive, and willing to learn</strong></p><p><strong>• Team player who likes dynamic environments</strong></p><p><strong>• Interested in personal growth and leadership exposure</strong></p><p><br /></p><p>✨ Fresh graduates & career switchers welcome</p><p>✨ Training provided from Day 1</p>",
